snippet.title: The 13th Doll: A Fan Game Of The 7th Guest Announcement Trailer!
snippet.description:
Pre Order now!  http://www.the13thdoll.com/_announcement.php
Return to The 7th Guest's Stauf Mansion very soon in The 13th Doll: A Fan Game Of The 7th Guest!  A licensed game made by fans of the original series!  Featuring 26 new puzzles, 2 playable characters and 5 unique endings!
